title Live Hacking Event State Transitions

[*] --> Draft : Organization creates event

Draft --> Published : Publish event
Draft --> [*] : Cancel draft

Published --> Registration_Open : Open for registration
Registration_Open --> Registration_Closed : Registration deadline
Registration_Closed --> Active : Event starts

Active --> In_Progress : Hacking begins
In_Progress --> Ending_Soon : 1 hour remaining
Ending_Soon --> Ended : Time expired

Ended --> Under_Review : Triage findings
Under_Review --> Results_Published : Winners announced
Results_Published --> Payment_Processing : Process rewards
Payment_Processing --> Completed : All payments done

Completed --> Archived : Archive after 30 days
Archived --> [*]

